ction</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A casual role-playing game where you play as a delivery person, busy organizing and delivering packages every day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play a one-stroke drawing mini-game – use a continuous line to pass through all traversable squares, from start to finish, and receive a package upon success.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After organizing the packages, personally delivering them to customers on the map might even lead to interesting stories.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When your stamina runs out, you need to rest. Once you're back to full strength, you can start sorting your inventory again.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872510/extras/2960008069b99929d3310f4dcdc15779.poster.avif?t=1768272754\" width=374 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872510/extras/2960008069b99929d3310f4dcdc15779.webm?t=1768272754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872510/extras/2960008069b99929d3310f4dcdc15779.mp4?t=1768272754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full Character Animation</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fun Puzzle Minigames</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trigger interesting short stories</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872510/extras/e74e4c62da8d6a470e5e2505360de1f4.poster.avif?t=1768272754\" width=374 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872510/extras/e74e4c62da8d6a470e5e2505360de1f4.webm?t=1768272754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872510/extras/e74e4c62da8d6a470e5e2505360de1f4.mp4?t=1768272754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mini-game gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a continuous, unbroken line to pass through all &quot;passable&quot; squares, from start to finish.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872510/extras/3df76b7ea331d551162baca933e58d3d.poster.avif?t=1768272754\" width=374 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872510/extras/3df76b7ea331d551162baca933e58d3d.webm?t=1768272754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872510/extras/3df76b7ea331d551162baca933e58d3d.mp4?t=1768272754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Technical Issues, Bug Reports, or Community Chat </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to our official Discord community.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can find the direct Discord link on the right-hand side of the Steam Store page.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Introduction</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A casual role-playing game where you play as a delivery person, busy organizing and delivering packages every day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play a one-stroke drawing mini-game – use a continuous line to pass through all traversable squares, from start to finish, and receive a package upon success.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragr